verbose_text: In addition, the levels of AAT and Dpt specific IgA in the NLFs of Group I at all time intervals, except at 30 minutes, were significantly higher than those of Group II (AAT; P = 0.003, P = 0.066, P = 0.035, and P = 0.009, respectively : Dpt specific IgA; P < 0.001, P = 0.074, P = 0.022, and P = 0.005, respectively) (XREF_FIG).
